config PANICOS_DEVICE_POWKIDDY_V90S
	bool "powkiddy/v90s (Allwinner A133)"
	select PANICOS_SOC_ALLWINNER_A133
	help
	  Powkiddy V90s — Allwinner A133 (quad-core Cortex-A53).
	  All kernel and bootloader components are pre-built blobs from the
	  vendor BSP. Build mode: blob-staging (no kernel/U-Boot compile).
	  Note: V90s ships a different kernel binary than V20 despite sharing
	  the same SoC and partition layout.
